		<h1 class="headline">A Bus Driver's Red Letter Day</h1>
										<span class="offScreen">By <span class="authors"><span class="author">The Daily Dish</span></span></span>
				<p class="metadata">
			<iframe id="facebookLike" src="http://www.facebook.com/plugins/like.php?href=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theatlantic.com%2Fdaily-dish%2Farchive%2F2010%2F05%2Fa-bus-drivers-red-letter-day%2F186890%2F&amp;layout=button_count&amp;width=125&amp;show_faces=false&amp;action=recommend&amp;font&amp;colorscheme=light&amp;height=21" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" style="border:none; overflow:hidden; height:21px; float:right; width:130px;" allowTransparency="true"></iframe>
			<span class="date last-child">May 19 2010, 10:57 AM ET</span>
				</p>
		
		<div class="articleContent">
		
						
		
					
			<p>In Denmark, Mukhtar the bus driver had a birthday. He worked that day. His regular passengers had an idea:</p><p><object width="510" height="385"><param name="movie" value="http://www.youtube.com/v/xgOyTNtsWyY&hl=en_US&fs=1&"></param><param name="allowFullScreen" value="true"></param><param name="allowscriptaccess" value="always"></param><embed src="http://www.youtube.com/v/xgOyTNtsWyY&hl=en_US&fs=1&" type="application/x-shockwave-flash" allowscriptaccess="always" allowfullscreen="true" width="510" height="385"></embed></object></p><br /><br />

			
						
		
			
		</div><!-- /blogEntryText -->

